### Create DayExercise (Admin only)
POST {{url}}/dayExercise
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "dayId": 1,
  "exerciseId": 2,
  "sets": 3,
  "reps": 12,
  "durationSeconds": 60
}

### Get all DayExercises (Public)
GET {{url}}/dayExercise
Content-Type: application/json

### Get DayExercises for a specific day (User role or higher)
GET {{url}}/dayExercise/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Update a DayExercise (Admin only)
PUT {{url}}/dayExercise/1/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "dayId": 1,
  "exerciseId": 2,
  "sets": 4,
  "reps": 15,
  "durationSeconds": 90
}

### Delete a DayExercise (Admin only)
DELETE {{url}}/dayExercise/1/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
